# Static images

**Canonical doc:** [docs/conventions/assets/static-images.md](../../docs/conventions/assets/static-images.md)

Do not use string paths like `"/tenants/logos/foo.png"` for bundled UI images — use static imports under `src/assets/` and `StaticImageData` with `next/image`. Run `npm run check:static-images` before PR.
